# Keep the weekly "concept" code on GitHub (.sql + .py).
# Everything else stays local: the roadmap brain, Medium blog drafts, LinkedIn posts.

# Ignore all markdown (roadmap, blogs, linkedin) — local only
*.md

# ...except the files we DO want published:
# (note: .gitignore does not support trailing inline comments)
!README.md
!interview/
!interview/*.md
!devops/
!devops/*.md
!articles/
!articles/*.md

# Python noise
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
.DS_Store
